ive, and it doesn’t forget.</mark></em></strong></span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">____________________________</mark></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>AUTHOR'S","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ZClP-g3z0nALXnkw7g3qe.webp","creator":"temto","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":3842,"messages":88436,"created_at":"2025-03-23T05:16:19.711986+00:00"}